{"tid":709360,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【最受歡迎馬匹】巴基之星得票大幅領先！排第二係……   #賽馬","createTime":"2018-06-20T02:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T02:46:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8e139f22a4b14b3d1c038beac5e354809aa6dabb","tid":709360,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:46:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/realtime/article/20180619/58337707\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180619%2F58337707&d=4p24QOPJguqBpXfAtBOJjL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=14036ed1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fracing%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180619%2F58337707&h=7ba1e582\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/racing/realtime/article/20180619/58337707</a><br />\n<br />\n【最受歡迎馬匹】巴基之星得票大幅領先！排第二係&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n16小時前18.2K<br />\n即時賽馬<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180619/large/1529402513_2523.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180619%2Flarge%2F1529402513_2523.jpg&h=b277b0a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴基之星(綠衫)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180619/large/1529401728_d678.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180619%2Flarge%2F1529401728_d678.jpg&h=c450dac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180619/large/1529401740_5aa8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180619%2Flarge%2F1529401740_5aa8.jpg&h=8521e531&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180619/large/1529401750_0825.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180619%2Flarge%2F1529401750_0825.jpg&h=fca26de5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2017/18年度馬季「最受歡迎馬匹」、「最受歡迎騎師」及「最受香港馬迷欣賞海外馬匹」的選期，6月27日便截止投票，馬會公佈截至6月18日(午夜)的投票走勢，「最受歡迎馬匹及騎師」分別由「巴基之星」及莫雷拉暫時領先，而「最受香港馬迷欣賞海外馬匹」則是「雲絲仙子」。<br />\n<br />\n「巴基之星」在「最受歡迎馬匹」選舉中，得票率暫為59.1%，大幅拋離第二位有18.2%的「美麗傳承」。而「最受歡迎騎師」莫雷拉有48.6%，第二位潘頓則只有33.1%。「最受香港馬迷欣賞海外馬匹」排第一的「雲絲仙子」有57.9%，領先有16.4%得票率的「高地之舞」。<br />\n<br />\n公眾可於6月27日或之前透過馬會網頁 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2yxCAgb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2yxCAgb&d=4p24QOPJguqBpXfAtBOJjL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a94c4fdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2yxCAgb</a> 進行投票，多間場外投注處亦設宣傳大使，協助公眾於網上投票。成功投票人士均自動進入大抽獎，幸運兒有機會贏取下列豐富獎品。<br />\n<br />\n頭獎：55&quot; The Frame UHD超高清電視 (名額1個)價值HK$29,880<br />\n<br />\n二獎：49&quot;QLED曲面遊戲專用顯示器 (名額1個)價值HK$14,880<br />\n<br />\n三獎：「馬場有禮」禮券一套總值港幣$1,500 (名額5個)價值HK$1,500/套"}]}